history.text: hi
would you please tell me the movie name
Hi. The movie is La La Land.
does it look like a good movie to watch? or a waste of time
I think it looks like a good movie to watch. It is a musical, and it is both a fantasy but also a depiction of the harsh reality of life.
a musical about the harsh reality of life.. you find that attractive>
I find it though provoking. And maybe I find harsh reality easier to take with a song and dance.
reality doesn't have to be harsh :P
Well, this is a romantic *comedy*. It's not that harsh. More bittersweet.
ok thanks a lot for the information
and thanks for chatting with me'
Are you interested in seeing the movie?
not so much

Do you like musicals? Or are you passionate about music? Because to a great extent, that is what the movie is about, people who are passionate about their art, and for one of the characters, that art is jazz.
i am indeed passionate about my art.and i do love music
maybe it is worth a try
do you know how to get the finish conversation button to come up?
I think there have to be a certain number exchanges for that button to come up. And I think it is timed.
well i create my own music and i love to do art
its possible i would like the movie
Anyway, I think the movie is definitely worth a try if you're into music and understand the passion for what you do.
One of the characters is desperately trying to "save" jazz, and risks everything for his art.
I prefer good rap music.
stuff with clean language and motivating

The other character (well, there are more than 2) is an actress, really trying to make it.
There's no rap, but there is kind of a fusion thing at one point.
the word fusion reminds me of dragonball
thats definitely appealing
I am not familiar with that.
i love dragonball, its about superheroes and extreme power
Not much like La La Land. Except for the power the characters have to make their dreams come true (or not, don't want to spoil it too much ;-) ).
thats why i do mturk. to make my dream come true
i want enough money in my bank to move to california
So I think you *would* relate to the characters in the movie, as they make sacrifices for their art... and live in California, hence the title, La La Land. ;-)
ok if its in california theres a 99% chance that i would like the movie
It's all about life in Los Angeles. The title refers to the nickname of the city, but also the kind of dreamworld that they characters live in.
ive been to los angeles
I have never been, but I am going this summer.
i want to move to sunnydale'
Isn't that the place in Buffy the Vampire Slayer?
Yup, i got a ring with buffys name on it
Cool. Is that a real place?
yes
Well, I hope your dreams come true. Good luck.
good luck to you as well, thanks for your time
And check out La La Land for inspiration!
check out dragonball for the nicest superheroes
Will do! Bye!
bye :)
